==Chinese==
===[[wikipedia:Taiwanese Mandarin|Taiwanese Mandarin]]===
*[[Pinyin]]: Jīanhùgōng 

===Noun===
'''[[監]][[護]][[工]]'''

[[caretaker]], [[in-house nurse]]. A job to take care of a disabled person's eating, moving, bathing, etc.. (Note: In Taiwan, the certificate required to be a nurse is higher than that required to be a "in-house nurse")

===Alternate forms===
[[监护工]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
===Related terms===
*看護工
*照顧服務員

